    "34494221": {
      "title": "Trust and partial typing in open systems of mobile agents",
      "abstract": "We present a partially-typed semantics for D¿, a distributed ¿-calculus. The semantics is designed for mobile agents in open distributed systems in which some sites may harbor malicious intentions. Nonetheless, the semantics guarantees traditional type-safety properties at \"good\" locations by using a mixture of static and dynamic type-checking. We show how the semantics can be extended to allow trust between sites, improving performance and expressiveness without compromising type-safety."
